  "properties": {
    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "## Understanding Your Users\r\n\r\nBefore designing your computer system, it's important to understand **who** will use it and **how** it will impact different people.\r\n\r\nChat with the AI to explore:\r\n- **Potential users** of your innovation\r\n- **Different needs and challenges** users might face\r\n- How your system can be more **accessible and effective**\r\n\r\nEven if you already have a project idea, this step will help you refine it by considering **diverse perspectives**. Start chatting to learn more about your users!",
    "aichat_settings": {
